{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program","slug":"daily-139-the-mentor-program","title":"The Mentor Program","title_ko":"멘토 프로그램","level":"B1","ageBand":"10-12","coverUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/cover.webp","summary_ko":"Jun은 학교 멘토 프로그램에 참가해 어린 학생을 돕고, 가르치는 일이 얼마나 보람 있는지 깨달아 간다.","wordCount":314,"stage":6,"collection":"daily","pages":[{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"On Monday, Ms. Park made an announcement.","translation_ko":"월요일에 박 선생님이 공지를 하셨다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"On","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"Monday","charStart":3,"charEnd":9,"startMs":280,"endMs":600},{"word":"Ms","charStart":11,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1120},{"word":"Park","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1480},{"word":"made","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1720},{"word":"an","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1720,"endMs":1920},{"word":"announcement","charStart":28,"charEnd":40,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2280}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Our school is starting a mentor program. Fifth graders will help second graders.\"","translation_ko":"\"우리 학교에서 멘토 프로그램을 시작합니다. 5학년이 2학년을 도와줄 거예요.\"","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Our","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"school","charStart":5,"charEnd":11,"startMs":380,"endMs":640},{"word":"is","charStart":12,"charEnd":14,"startMs":640,"endMs":980},{"word":"starting","charStart":15,"charEnd":23,"startMs":980,"endMs":1160},{"word":"a","charStart":24,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1620},{"word":"mentor","charStart":26,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1660},{"word":"program","charStart":33,"charEnd":40,"startMs":1660,"endMs":2400},{"word":"Fifth","charStart":42,"charEnd":47,"startMs":2900,"endMs":3000},{"word":"graders","charStart":48,"charEnd":55,"startMs":3000,"endMs":3300},{"word":"will","charStart":56,"charEnd":60,"startMs":3300,"endMs":3600},{"word":"help","charStart":61,"charEnd":65,"startMs":3600,"endMs":3800},{"word":"second","charStart":66,"charEnd":72,"startMs":3800,"endMs":4100},{"word":"graders","charStart":73,"charEnd":80,"startMs":4100,"endMs":4340}]}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"Jun felt nervous. He had never taught anyone before.","translation_ko":"준은 긴장했다. 누군가를 가르쳐 본 적이 없었기 때문이다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"felt","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":460,"endMs":1180},{"word":"nervous","charStart":9,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1840},{"word":"He","charStart":18,"charEnd":20,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2560},{"word":"had","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2800},{"word":"never","charStart":25,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2800,"endMs":3140},{"word":"taught","charStart":31,"charEnd":37,"startMs":3140,"endMs":3620},{"word":"anyone","charStart":38,"charEnd":44,"startMs":3620,"endMs":4120},{"word":"before","charStart":45,"charEnd":51,"startMs":4120,"endMs":4540}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"Mina leaned over and whispered, \"I think it sounds exciting!\"","translation_ko":"미나가 몸을 기울이며 속삭였다. \"나는 재미있을 것 같아!\"","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Mina","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"leaned","charStart":5,"charEnd":11,"startMs":440,"endMs":820},{"word":"over","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":820,"endMs":1180},{"word":"and","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1700},{"word":"whispered","charStart":21,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1700,"endMs":2160},{"word":"I","charStart":33,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2640},{"word":"think","charStart":35,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2640,"endMs":2840},{"word":"it","charStart":41,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2840,"endMs":3160},{"word":"sounds","charStart":44,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3360},{"word":"exciting","charStart":51,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3360,"endMs":3860}]}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"After class, Ms. Park spoke to them.","translation_ko":"수업 후, 박 선생님이 두 사람에게 말씀하셨다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"After","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"class","charStart":6,"charEnd":11,"startMs":320,"endMs":780},{"word":"Ms","charStart":13,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1340},{"word":"Park","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1600},{"word":"spoke","charStart":22,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1880},{"word":"to","charStart":28,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2080},{"word":"them","charStart":31,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2220}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"I chose you because you are patient and kind,\" she said.","translation_ko":"\"너희를 뽑은 건 인내심이 있고 친절하기 때문이에요,\" 선생님이 말씀하셨다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"I","charStart":1,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":640},{"word":"chose","charStart":3,"charEnd":8,"startMs":640,"endMs":980},{"word":"you","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":980,"endMs":1240},{"word":"because","charStart":13,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1560},{"word":"you","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1740},{"word":"are","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1740,"endMs":1920},{"word":"patient","charStart":29,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2300},{"word":"and","charStart":37,"charEnd":40,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2540},{"word":"kind","charStart":41,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2540,"endMs":3220},{"word":"she","charStart":48,"charEnd":51,"startMs":3220,"endMs":3340},{"word":"said","charStart":52,"charEnd":56,"startMs":3340,"endMs":3600}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p3-s3","ord":2,"text":"\"A good mentor listens just as much as she talks.\"","translation_ko":"\"좋은 멘토는 말하는 만큼 잘 들어야 해요.\"","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p3-s3.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":1,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":180},{"word":"good","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":180,"endMs":460},{"word":"mentor","charStart":8,"charEnd":14,"startMs":460,"endMs":900},{"word":"listens","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":900,"endMs":1480},{"word":"just","charStart":23,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1800},{"word":"as","charStart":28,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2080},{"word":"much","charStart":31,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2200},{"word":"as","charStart":36,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2420},{"word":"she","charStart":39,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2580},{"word":"talks","charStart":43,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2920}]}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"On Tuesday, Jun met his student, a second grader named Soo.","translation_ko":"화요일에 준은 멘티인 2학년 Soo를 만났다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"On","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"Tuesday","charStart":3,"charEnd":10,"startMs":240,"endMs":700},{"word":"Jun","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1440},{"word":"met","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1660},{"word":"his","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1660,"endMs":1860},{"word":"student","charStart":24,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2180},{"word":"a","charStart":33,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2660},{"word":"second","charStart":35,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2660,"endMs":2880},{"word":"grader","charStart":42,"charEnd":48,"startMs":2880,"endMs":3200},{"word":"named","charStart":49,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3200,"endMs":3440},{"word":"Soo","charStart":55,"charEnd":58,"startMs":3440,"endMs":3720}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"Soo looked shy and kept staring at the desk.","translation_ko":"Soo는 수줍어 보였고 계속 책상만 내려다봤다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Soo","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"looked","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":460,"endMs":760},{"word":"shy","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":760,"endMs":1180},{"word":"and","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1660},{"word":"kept","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1660,"endMs":1860},{"word":"staring","charStart":24,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2200},{"word":"at","charStart":32,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2400},{"word":"the","charStart":35,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2400,"endMs":2520},{"word":"desk","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2520,"endMs":2780}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p4-s3","ord":2,"text":"Jun smiled and said, \"I was nervous too. Let's start slowly.\"","translation_ko":"준이 웃으며 말했다. \"나도 긴장했었어. 천천히 시작하자.\"","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p4-s3.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Jun","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":760},{"word":"smiled","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":760,"endMs":1260},{"word":"and","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1600},{"word":"said","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1820},{"word":"I","charStart":22,"charEnd":23,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2300},{"word":"was","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2560},{"word":"nervous","charStart":28,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2820},{"word":"too","charStart":36,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2820,"endMs":3220},{"word":"Let's","charStart":41,"charEnd":46,"startMs":3680,"endMs":3980},{"word":"start","charStart":47,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3980,"endMs":4200},{"word":"slowly","charStart":53,"charEnd":59,"startMs":4200,"endMs":4560}]}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"They practiced reading together for thirty minutes.","translation_ko":"두 사람은 30분 동안 함께 읽기 연습을 했다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"They","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":480},{"word":"practiced","charStart":5,"charEnd":14,"startMs":480,"endMs":1040},{"word":"reading","charStart":15,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1460},{"word":"together","charStart":23,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1840},{"word":"for","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2160},{"word":"thirty","charStart":36,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2600},{"word":"minutes","charStart":43,"charEnd":50,"startMs":2600,"endMs":2940}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"Soo made mistakes, but Jun stayed calm.","translation_ko":"Soo가 실수를 했지만, 준은 차분함을 유지했다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Soo","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":780},{"word":"made","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":780,"endMs":1020},{"word":"mistakes","charStart":9,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1600},{"word":"but","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2300},{"word":"Jun","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2520},{"word":"stayed","charStart":27,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2520,"endMs":2880},{"word":"calm","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2880,"endMs":3220}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p5-s3","ord":2,"text":"\"Good try! Let's read that sentence one more time,\" he said.","translation_ko":"\"잘했어! 그 문장 한 번 더 읽어 보자,\" 준이 말했다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p5-s3.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Good","charStart":1,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":200},{"word":"try","charStart":6,"charEnd":9,"startMs":200,"endMs":620},{"word":"Let's","charStart":11,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1160,"endMs":1340},{"word":"read","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1460},{"word":"that","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1740},{"word":"sentence","charStart":27,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2080},{"word":"one","charStart":36,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2560},{"word":"more","charStart":40,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2780},{"word":"time","charStart":45,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2780,"endMs":3100},{"word":"he","charStart":52,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3360,"endMs":3520},{"word":"said","charStart":55,"charEnd":59,"startMs":3520,"endMs":3760}]}]},{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"daily-139-the-mentor-program-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"The next day, Mina told Jun her student kept asking the same question.","translation_ko":"다음 날, 미나는 멘티가 같은 질문을 계속 한다고 말했다.","audioUrl":"/seed/daily-139-the-mentor-program/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":160},{"word":"next","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":160,"endMs":420},{"word":"day","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":420,"endMs":780},{"word":"Mina","charStart":14,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1240},{"word":"told","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1600},{"word":"Jun","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1940},{"word":"her","charStart":28,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2220},{"word":"student","charStart":32,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2540},{"word":"kept","charStart":4